metadata.name: OJUJU
metadata.description:
Ojuju is the introductory piece in the Ojuju Saga series. We are welcomed into the grasp of the Ojuju, evil masquerades whose name strikes fear into the heart of men. They are a focal point in this series as they symbolize the various obstacles and challenges we always come across in life.

"Be on guard ,for the Ojuju comes at night"

This piece is also serves as a celebratory piece for my acceptance into SuperRare and will serve as the foundation for more to come as the series progress.
